sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API
    participant S3
    participant Cache
    participant Bedrock
    
    User->>API: Submit Application (Form + Files)
    API->>S3: Store Documents (Chunked if >25MB)
    API->>Cache: Check for Cached Policies
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>API: Return Cached Policies
    else Cache Miss
        API->>Bedrock: Extract Policy Requirements
        Bedrock-->>API: Return Requirements
        API->>Cache: Store Results
    end
    API->>Bedrock: Validate Application (Multi-Step)
    Bedrock-->>API: Return Validation Result
    API->>User: Return PDF Report
    